30:57.278 --> 30:58.309
He's here.

31:05.987 --> 31:08.108
The centerpiece of our exhibit.

31:08.237 --> 31:11.603
Napoleon had three priceless diamonds set into the hilt of his sword.

31:11.737 --> 31:14.819
After his defeat, they were pried out and dispersed around the globe.

31:14.946 --> 31:18.810
This is one of the rare occasions the last
remaining diamond is on public display.

31:18.946 --> 31:21.517
And next, we have some rare Egyptian gems.

31:50.239 --> 31:51.816
Cute little rock.

31:51.948 --> 31:53.606
I'm just here to look.

31:53.740 --> 31:54.818
Just as well.

31:54.948 --> 31:58.195
With six cameras-- four stationary, two revolving,

31:58.323 --> 31:59.982
a dozen I.R. motion sensors--

32:00.115 --> 32:02.734
Sixteen.
You missed the ones at ankle level.

32:02.865 --> 32:05.270
Plus your standard 24-hour rotating guards.

32:05.407 --> 32:07.860
Unbreakable polycarbonate display,

32:07.990 --> 32:10.739
controlled by an uncopyable magnetic key card.

32:12.657 --> 32:16.698
I just realized--
you could never get it anyway.

32:20.199 --> 32:21.396
You're right.

32:22.616 --> 32:24.441
When you're right, you're right.

32:25.241 --> 32:26.520
It's impossible.

33:12.952 --> 33:14.279
Give me a ride.

33:14.411 --> 33:15.524
I don't think so.

33:15.661 --> 33:17.782
Maybe you should think again.

33:43.412 --> 33:47.453
May I present Monsieur Henri Mooré.

33:48.121 --> 33:49.448
Mr. Burdett.

33:50.121 --> 33:51.661
It is a pleasure to meet you, sir.

33:51.788 --> 33:53.613
Oh, you're an American.

33:53.746 --> 33:56.235
Hmm. Henri Mooré?

33:56.371 --> 33:58.278
Ah. My name is Henry Moore.

33:58.413 --> 34:00.818
I placed the thing on the "e".

34:00.955 --> 34:02.910
I felt it more appropriate to my surroundings.

34:03.038 --> 34:04.910
- Oh.
- Please.

34:09.496 --> 34:10.989
I imagine you're wondering why you're here.

34:11.121 --> 34:12.994
Well...

34:13.121 --> 34:15.445
Forgive Jean-Paul's tactics, Mr. Burdett,

34:15.580 --> 34:20.036
but to put it bluntly, the impoverished people of this island need your help.

34:20.164 --> 34:21.572
Hmm.

34:21.706 --> 34:24.621
Five years ago, I was a successful businessman in Detroit.

34:24.748 --> 34:26.822
While vacationing on this island,

34:26.956 --> 34:28.994
I was sitting on the beach drinking a...

34:29.123 --> 34:30.913
Citron martini.

34:33.956 --> 34:34.777
I don't recall what I was

34:34.804 --> 34:35.853
drinking-- it's not important.

34:35.956 --> 34:37.697
But I experienced a revelation--

34:37.831 --> 34:41.871
that I had been brought to this island to provide the commensurate social services

34:41.998 --> 34:45.161
that were sadly lacking for the poorer elements of society here.

34:45.331 --> 34:48.199
And you want me to buy a table at your next fundraiser.

34:49.873 --> 34:51.071
No, Mr. Burdett.

34:51.206 --> 34:52.996
But I am offering you the opportunity

34:53.123 --> 34:55.956
to participate in the vital growth of my infrastructure.

34:56.083 --> 34:57.362
Uh-huh. How's that?

34:57.999 --> 34:59.871
I want you to steal me that diamond.

35:02.791 --> 35:03.988
I'm not a criminal.

35:04.125 --> 35:06.364
Right. Neither am I.

35:06.500 --> 35:07.957
Good.
Then we understand each other.

35:08.083 --> 35:09.457
- Yes.
- Yeah.

35:09.583 --> 35:11.657
Let me show you around, Mr. Burdett.

35:15.167 --> 35:17.738
Do you think it fair that the indigenous of this island

35:17.875 --> 35:20.625
are not allowed to enter the casinos unless they work there?

35:22.126 --> 35:24.496
Why is it that only the rich should enjoy

35:24.626 --> 35:28.785
pharmaceutically-assisted moments of personal introspection?

35:28.918 --> 35:32.579
The safety and security found in owning your own machine gun.

35:33.668 --> 35:34.912
The pleasures derived

35:35.043 --> 35:39.286
from financially-procured female companionship.

35:41.585 --> 35:44.749
The underprivileged should not be denied these essential diversions.

35:44.877 --> 35:47.117
I mean, look around you, Mr. Burdett.

35:47.252 --> 35:48.793
No one is turned away.

35:49.627 --> 35:52.376
All I do, I do for the people.

35:52.502 --> 35:53.995
And why do you need the diamond for that?

35:54.794 --> 35:58.325
I have an urgent need to expand my humanitarian program.

35:58.461 --> 36:01.661
A cash injection in the tens of millions of dollars

36:01.794 --> 36:03.536
would relieve the entire Caribbean.

36:05.711 --> 36:08.460
What I'm suggesting is a partnership, Mr. Burdett.

36:08.586 --> 36:10.743
You are a stranger to this island.

36:10.878 --> 36:12.786
I can give you what you don't have--

36:12.920 --> 36:18.953
access to the marina, the crews, rotation schedules, whatever you need.

36:43.963 --> 36:46.037
I couldn't sleep.
Didn't wanna wake you.

36:47.422 --> 36:49.792
I saw you on the ship yesterday.

36:52.214 --> 36:55.165
I had a feeling you might be there, too.

37:01.839 --> 37:04.506
Don't you ever feel we weren't quite finished?

37:06.631 --> 37:09.914
Look, Max, I miss it, too.

37:11.090 --> 37:12.915
We were great.

37:13.048 --> 37:16.331
And we went out at the top of our game, undefeated.

37:16.465 --> 37:18.752
The best time to quit.

37:19.507 --> 37:21.048
Maybe.

37:23.715 --> 37:25.256
Max, I cased it.

37:25.382 --> 37:28.878
It's not a one man job, and there's no way you're pulling me into it.

37:29.007 --> 37:30.381
We're retired.

37:30.507 --> 37:33.671
Now the challenge is to find joy in simple things.

37:33.799 --> 37:36.335
And I like that challenge.

38:05.051 --> 38:06.046
Yeah?

38:06.176 --> 38:07.171
I lied on the ship.

38:07.301 --> 38:08.675
I <i>could</i> get it.

38:08.801 --> 38:09.796
<i>Here's how.</i>

38:09.926 --> 38:12.497
<i>I'd cut the camera feed and go in from behind the exhibit.</i>

38:12.635 --> 38:15.549
It's blowable from the storage room, and I'd do it after 10 p.m.

38:15.677 --> 38:17.253
Why?

38:17.385 --> 38:20.217
The retired arthritic cops always get that shift.

38:21.219 --> 38:23.126
So that's how you do it.

38:23.260 --> 38:24.670
And now I've told you.

38:24.802 --> 38:26.840
So now I can't.

38:38.803 --> 38:40.379
Oh, my God.

38:40.511 --> 38:42.585
- What are you doing?
- I'm cooking.

38:42.720 --> 38:44.757
- Since when?
- This morning.

38:44.886 --> 38:46.509
We are decent law-abiding people,

38:46.637 --> 38:49.551
and decent law-abiding people cook omelets for breakfast.

38:50.470 --> 38:51.500
Oh.

38:52.470 --> 38:53.797
State your business.

38:53.929 --> 38:55.303
<i>You almost had me last night</i>

38:55.429 --> 38:58.711
<i>with that old David Copperfield smoke and mirrors trick.</i>

38:58.846 --> 39:03.005
"Look at my assistant with the big tits while
I take the Rolex right off your wrist."

39:03.137 --> 39:04.168
What do you want about her?

39:04.304 --> 39:06.094
I wanna know how you're really gonna do it,

39:06.221 --> 39:09.219
and you're gonna tell me while we're fishing.

39:09.346 --> 39:10.460
Fishing?

39:10.596 --> 39:11.875
I don't fish.

39:12.013 --> 39:13.885
I got a boat stacked with beer.

39:14.013 --> 39:15.008
Drink it yourself.

39:15.138 --> 39:16.033
<i>You might as well come.</i>

39:16.060 --> 39:16.954
<i>You're paying for it.</i>

39:17.055 --> 39:18.844
<i>I charged it to my suite.</i>

39:18.972 --> 39:21.507
All the same, Stanley, I'll pass.

39:21.638 --> 39:22.633
There is an option.

39:22.763 --> 39:26.544
I get the local police to bring you down to the station, we sweat you there.

39:26.680 --> 39:27.842
<i>And I do mean sweat.</i>

39:27.972 --> 39:31.302
<i>There's no air conditioning, so dress light.</i>

39:31.431 --> 39:33.303
The eggs on this island taste funny.

39:33.431 --> 39:35.836
They must have some weird chickens.

39:38.639 --> 39:39.836
<i>What'll it be, Max?</i>

39:39.973 --> 39:41.003
I'll see you soon.

39:50.765 --> 39:53.929
Tell me this isn't better than standing in some lineup.

39:54.932 --> 39:56.389
I've never been in a lineup.

40:03.141 --> 40:05.546
Ooh, that's a hell of a watch.

40:05.682 --> 40:06.879
What's that kind of thing run you?

40:07.016 --> 40:09.053
A couple of grand.

40:11.349 --> 40:14.431
Why don't you pick one up on the Bureau's expense account?

40:14.558 --> 40:17.556
Oh, they keep me on a real tight leash.

40:17.683 --> 40:19.306
I got you to thank for that.

40:19.433 --> 40:20.807
Ah.

40:22.142 --> 40:23.682
Whoo! It's cookin' out here.

40:26.642 --> 40:28.763
So if I didn't shoot you, where'd you get the screen door?

40:31.309 --> 40:32.802
Knitting accident.

40:45.059 --> 40:46.931
Dab some of this on my back, will you?

40:47.518 --> 40:48.596
Are you serious?

40:48.726 --> 40:50.321
Yeah. I've got delicate skin.

40:50.348 --> 40:51.501
I don't wanna burn.

40:57.852 --> 41:00.969
I bet you were the best kid in the neighborhood at hide-and-seek, huh?

41:01.102 --> 41:02.346
So you joined the Bureau.

41:02.477 --> 41:04.764
Yeah, I found them all.

41:06.519 --> 41:08.225
No one ever found me.

41:09.061 --> 41:13.268
Once I found a good spot, I'd stay there for days.

41:16.770 --> 41:18.097
There you go.

41:18.228 --> 41:20.302
Now, turn around.
I'll do you.

41:20.436 --> 41:21.467
I'll handle it.

41:21.603 --> 41:23.393
No, come on.
You're gonna burn.

41:32.437 --> 41:33.551
Good.

41:34.645 --> 41:35.640
Okay.

41:35.771 --> 41:37.477
There. That's good.

41:37.604 --> 41:39.346
Wait. Don't you want me to coat everything?

41:39.479 --> 41:40.888
That's good. My pole.

41:41.021 --> 41:42.679
No way, man!
I'm only doing your back!

41:42.813 --> 41:43.807
My pole!

41:43.938 --> 41:45.217
Hey, we got something.
Come on.

41:45.354 --> 41:46.349
Oh, oh, oh. Look at this!

41:46.479 --> 41:48.221
Oh. We got something here, Stanley.

41:48.355 --> 41:49.349
Ooh! Aah!

41:49.480 --> 41:51.435
Shit! Come on!

41:51.563 --> 41:53.104
Come on!
Help me pull it up.

41:53.230 --> 41:55.102
Don't lose it, don't lose it!

41:58.105 --> 41:59.432
- It's a monster.
- We can do it!

41:59.563 --> 42:01.601
This is big.
Okay, come on, pull!

42:01.730 --> 42:03.140
- Are <i>you</i> pulling?
- I'm pulling, man.

42:03.272 --> 42:04.267
Jesus Christ!

42:04.397 --> 42:07.099
Stanley!
One, two, three!

42:07.231 --> 42:09.056
Oh! Aah!

42:09.939 --> 42:10.934
Jesus Christ!

42:11.064 --> 42:12.640
It's a shark, it's a shark.

42:12.772 --> 42:13.767
Yeah.

42:15.773 --> 42:17.265
Why is it not moving?

42:17.398 --> 42:18.280
Maybe it's in shock.

42:18.307 --> 42:19.498
What do you wanna do?

42:19.606 --> 42:20.673
Maybe it's dead.

42:20.700 --> 42:22.299
I mean, it looks dead.

42:23.981 --> 42:25.143
Go over and shake it.

42:25.273 --> 42:27.430
- Why me?
- Well, you're FBI.

42:27.565 --> 42:28.974
What's that have to do with anything?

42:29.107 --> 42:31.856
If it bites your arm off, you get disability for the rest of your life.

42:31.982 --> 42:33.226
- Go!
- <i>You</i> hooked it.

42:33.357 --> 42:34.387
<i>You</i> go see if it's alive.

42:34.524 --> 42:36.100
<i>Yeah, I hooked it, so you go see if it's alive.</i>

42:36.232 --> 42:37.476
- Go!
- Hey, hey!

42:37.607 --> 42:40.440
Oh, okay.
Here I go.

42:41.691 --> 42:43.480
I'm just gonna sneak up on it.

42:44.232 --> 42:45.227
Why are you whispering?

42:45.358 --> 42:47.099
So it won't know the plan.

42:48.024 --> 42:49.482
Hey.

42:56.066 --> 42:57.310
- Aah!
- Aah! Shit!

42:57.442 --> 42:58.851
Watch out, watch out, watch out!

43:03.525 --> 43:06.440
You have the right to remain silent!

43:07.650 --> 43:08.812
Yeah, it's dead.

43:11.859 --> 43:13.482
Yeah.

43:37.444 --> 43:38.438
Look at them.

43:38.569 --> 43:41.816
If you didn't know any better, you'd think they were friends.

43:41.944 --> 43:43.769
You must be Lola.

43:44.527 --> 43:45.522
Sophie?

43:46.486 --> 43:47.599
Nice gun.

43:47.736 --> 43:49.063
Sig Sauer P228.

43:49.194 --> 43:50.984
Custom trigger action.

43:51.111 --> 43:52.189
Oh.

43:52.319 --> 43:53.896
- Nice shoes.
- Thank you.

43:54.028 --> 43:56.149
- Chanel?
- Cruz collection.

43:58.195 --> 43:59.652
How bad was it?

44:00.528 --> 44:02.104
Oh, not too bad.

44:03.862 --> 44:05.189
Sophie seems nice.

44:05.987 --> 44:07.231
Yeah, for a cop.

44:08.487 --> 44:10.193
Lola seems cool.

44:10.320 --> 44:11.434
For a thief.

44:26.696 --> 44:28.106
Yes!

44:33.322 --> 44:34.731
I resign. You win.

44:34.863 --> 44:36.191
Make a wish.

44:36.322 --> 44:38.194
Okay.

44:38.322 --> 44:41.486
I wish you'd write your vows.

44:54.864 --> 44:56.144
<i>I'm so tense.</i>

44:56.281 --> 44:56.997
<i>Come here.</i>

44:57.024 --> 44:58.381
<i>Let me relax you.</i>

44:58.490 --> 44:59.406
<i>What are you doing?</i>

44:59.433 --> 45:01.265
<i>Why are you taking off your clothes?</i>

45:01.365 --> 45:02.360
Now we're talkin'.

45:02.490 --> 45:04.031
<i>Are you being naughty?</i>

45:04.157 --> 45:05.697
<i>Naughty enough to spank.</i>

45:05.823 --> 45:08.146
Oh, yeah!

45:08.282 --> 45:11.233
<i>I'll bite you.
Can I bite you?</i>

45:11.365 --> 45:13.854
<i>The door.
Are we expecting anyone?</i>

45:13.990 --> 45:16.028
<i>Yeah. A friend.</i>

45:16.157 --> 45:17.780
<i>- A friend?
- A friend?</i>

45:17.907 --> 45:19.104
<i>A girlfriend.</i>

45:19.241 --> 45:20.236
<i>You didn't.</i>

45:20.366 --> 45:21.775
<i>I love you, baby.</i>

45:21.908 --> 45:24.443
<i>You know I'll do anything for you.</i>

45:26.908 --> 45:27.938
<i>Wait here.</i>

45:28.075 --> 45:29.567
<i>What's she gonna do?</i>

45:31.033 --> 45:33.024
Tell him.
Tell him.

45:33.158 --> 45:35.232
<i>She's gonna help me relax you.</i>

45:35.367 --> 45:36.859
<i>You're kidding.</i>

45:37.658 --> 45:38.689
Nice.

45:38.825 --> 45:40.366
<i>You're gonna like this.</i>

45:40.492 --> 45:41.736
Lucky bastard.

45:41.867 --> 45:43.905
- <i>Who is she?</i>
- <i>You'll see.</i>

45:44.575 --> 45:48.652
<i>Max, I'd like you to meet Stan's mom.</i>

45:56.368 --> 45:57.481
<i>Night, Stan.</i>

46:01.493 --> 46:02.690
Son of a...

46:59.538 --> 47:01.279
You're only in port 48 more hours.

47:01.413 --> 47:03.071
Stay on high alert.

47:03.205 --> 47:06.072
Agent Lloyd, we have the most sophisticated security system

47:06.205 --> 47:08.658
ever installed on a seagoing vessel.

47:08.788 --> 47:10.115
And you'll need it.

47:10.872 --> 47:12.069
Excuse me, sir.

47:13.080 --> 47:14.952
There's been a security breach.

47:39.415 --> 47:40.493
Don't move!

47:42.957 --> 47:43.952
Turn around.

47:46.290 --> 47:47.404
Turn around!

47:50.249 --> 47:51.279
