49:41.796 --> 49:44.581
Maybe not with a woman, but with a diamond.

49:45.380 --> 49:46.375
You want her.

49:46.505 --> 49:48.460
And I'm jealous.

49:48.588 --> 49:50.544
You've got nothing to worry about.

49:50.672 --> 49:52.462
Where were you tonight, Max?

49:52.589 --> 49:56.417
I've been home, writing my vows.

49:56.547 --> 49:57.542
Oh! Let me see.

49:57.672 --> 50:00.670
Sorry.
You have to wait.

50:01.714 --> 50:03.752
Well, I'm not gonna let that little bitch take my man.

50:03.881 --> 50:05.504
I'm gonna fight for what's mine.

50:05.631 --> 50:06.661
Really?

50:06.798 --> 50:09.121
And how exactly are you gonna do that?

50:09.256 --> 50:10.797
I'm a thief.

50:11.798 --> 50:14.168
I know a thing or two about distraction.

50:19.673 --> 50:22.292
It's a beautiful jewel, Max.

50:23.340 --> 50:27.464
But I guarantee you, it's no fun in the tub.

50:30.216 --> 50:31.756
Mmm.

50:32.507 --> 50:35.210
I had him.
You shoulda stayed out of my way.

50:35.341 --> 50:37.664
I didn't want you to get hurt.
I'm sorry.

50:37.799 --> 50:39.288
You're the one who's hurt.

50:39.315 --> 50:40.574
You should ice that.

50:40.674 --> 50:42.961
Why are men always trying to protect women?

50:43.633 --> 50:44.877
'Cause you smell good.

50:45.008 --> 50:46.631
It's all about sex, isn't it?

50:46.758 --> 50:49.329
Why can't we just be two cops working a case?

50:49.467 --> 50:51.090
Hey, I happen to agree with you.

50:51.217 --> 50:53.207
From now on, we're just partners on this.

50:53.342 --> 50:54.455
Fine.

50:54.592 --> 50:56.832
- So, let's have dinner and discuss it.
- No, thanks.

50:56.967 --> 50:58.294
How about a steam?

50:58.425 --> 51:01.791
What-- I-- no, I always steam with my partners.

51:02.592 --> 51:05.046
Okay, you wanna go for a Jacuzzi, partner?

51:05.176 --> 51:07.629
I have a big tub in my room.

51:20.802 --> 51:22.342
We have to talk.

51:22.468 --> 51:25.135
Max. Great timing.
Ride with us.

51:25.260 --> 51:26.883
Can we just do this one on one?

51:27.010 --> 51:28.384
Oh, of course.

51:30.135 --> 51:33.169
<i>California dreaming...</i>

51:33.302 --> 51:36.798
Are you familiar with the pleasures of anonymous love, Max?

51:38.344 --> 51:39.339
No.

51:40.428 --> 51:44.089
Recently I found myself experimenting with alternative lifestyle parameters

51:44.220 --> 51:46.376
based largely on the free love philosophy

51:46.511 --> 51:49.509
as found in the collected works of The Mamas and The Papas.

51:50.762 --> 51:52.338
I never made that connection.

51:52.470 --> 51:53.548
Oh, it's there.

51:53.678 --> 51:56.381
That Michelle Phillips, she could walk it like she talked it.

51:56.512 --> 51:58.798
Earl, burn one of my CDs for Max.

51:58.929 --> 52:00.421
Yes, sir.

52:12.596 --> 52:14.053
This is it, Max.

52:14.179 --> 52:15.459
My vision.

52:16.346 --> 52:18.917
My infrastructure growing before our eyes.

52:19.805 --> 52:20.883
It used to be a children's hospital,

52:21.013 --> 52:24.841
but I'm revitalizing it into a paramilitary training facility.

52:24.972 --> 52:28.633
More importantly, that ship is leaving in two days.

52:32.264 --> 52:33.259
What's this?

52:33.389 --> 52:34.716
Everything you need.

52:35.347 --> 52:37.468
Schematics, detailed plan.

52:37.597 --> 52:39.588
You can do it yourself.

52:41.306 --> 52:43.261
Go in through the air conditioning vents.

52:43.389 --> 52:46.222
The exhibit is accessible from the storage facility behind it.

52:46.348 --> 52:49.548
There's cameras there, so you're gonna have to cut the central feed.

52:49.681 --> 52:51.340
Red wires in the control panel here.

52:51.473 --> 52:54.673
If you don't cut the red wire, they'll see everything.

52:54.807 --> 52:57.378
- What next?
- Blow the wall.

52:57.515 --> 52:58.842
- C-4?
- Uh-uh.

52:58.974 --> 53:01.676
I'd use a shape charge with a detonation cord.

53:01.807 --> 53:04.177
Smaller but more effective.

53:04.307 --> 53:08.431
And... you'd wanna blow it after 10 p.m.

53:08.557 --> 53:11.591
- Why is that?
- Graveyard shift.

53:11.724 --> 53:14.391
Always the retired cops with arthritis.

53:14.516 --> 53:16.174
That's how I'd do it.

53:17.516 --> 53:18.974
Then that's how I'll do it.

53:22.350 --> 53:24.554
You know, we're not partners anymore, Max.

53:25.308 --> 53:27.844
In fact, you see me, cross the street.

