Good afternoon. Atlantis.
How may I help?

54:19.269 --> 54:21.556
Mr. Lloyd,
the Bridge Suite, please.

54:23.061 --> 54:24.139
<i>Hello.</i>

54:24.270 --> 54:25.597
<i>- Stanley.
- Yeah.</i>

54:25.728 --> 54:27.140
<i>It's Max, just checking in.</i>

54:27.167 --> 54:28.421
<i>Cut the crap, Max.</i>

54:28.520 --> 54:30.843
<i>You're making sure I'm in my room and not following you.</i>

54:30.978 --> 54:33.763
How could you be following me if you're in your room?

54:33.895 --> 54:36.265
