Hello!

56:18.942 --> 56:19.937
What?

56:21.359 --> 56:22.354
What?

56:22.484 --> 56:25.648
If you're gonna forward your calls, don't tail me so close.

56:31.235 --> 56:32.432
Aah!

57:44.989 --> 57:46.529
Hey.

57:46.655 --> 57:48.445
I heard the call over the radio.

57:48.572 --> 57:51.736
Every year there's one white boy that goes down at Junkanoo.

57:52.572 --> 57:53.865
Here's what I found out.

57:53.892 --> 57:54.968
Max closed escrow,

57:55.073 --> 57:57.691
and then a month later the cruise booked the diamond.

57:57.823 --> 58:00.109
- Maybe he <i>is</i> retired.
