58:16.032 --> 58:17.110
Better?

58:18.032 --> 58:19.525
There's another one here.

58:22.116 --> 58:23.194
Now?

58:23.324 --> 58:25.611
This one's particularly painful.

58:29.366 --> 58:31.406
There's some referred pain.

58:31.433 --> 58:33.849
It's somewhere around... here.

58:38.033 --> 58:40.237
I'll have to get hurt more often.

58:40.367 --> 58:42.737
And in more interesting places.

59:03.243 --> 59:05.648
- Oh, God, I'm vibrating!
- So am I.

59:05.785 --> 59:08.404
No. No, no.

59:08.535 --> 59:10.572
- I'm getting a call.
- What?

59:10.702 --> 59:12.776
Is nothing sacred?

59:12.910 --> 59:13.988
Shit, I have to go.

59:14.118 --> 59:15.373
Go? No, you can't go.

59:15.400 --> 59:17.012
I just unwrapped my head.

59:17.119 --> 59:18.742
Sorry, I need a rain check.

59:18.869 --> 59:19.975
